<para id="fs-idm389091408"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67840"/>For each of the following ten independent transactions, provide a written description of what occurred in each transaction. <link document="m67839" target-id="OSX_Acct_F02_02_GraphEqn"/> might help you.</para>
